# stable-browser-fingerprint

**Stable & lightweight browser fingerprinting for the modern web.**

Generate the **same unique fingerprint** for the same browser/device — even if the user clears their cache, cookies, localStorage, or uses incognito mode.

### Features
- Works after clearing browser data
- High stability on the same device (Canvas + WebGL + Audio + hardware signals)
- Good distinction between phones vs desktops and different hardware
- Zero dependencies
- TypeScript support with full types
- Small bundle size
- No storage used (pure client-side)

### Why "Stable"?
Most fingerprint libraries change when the browser updates or user travels. This package focuses on **hardware + rendering signals** that remain consistent longer, while still providing strong uniqueness.

Perfect for:
- "Remember this device" features
- Fraud & bot detection
- Account security & session binding
- Analytics without cookies
